	<img src="/images/lincoln-pre-glue.jpg" alt="hand and adapter" />
	<img src="/images/lincoln-post-glue.jpg" alt="hand and adapater together" />
</figure>

<p><img src="/images/lincoln-spin.gif" alt="spinning gif of combined version" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Install it.</li>
</ul>

